descp2: Non-negative integer, the number of out-of-vocabulary buckets. All out-of-vocabulary inputs will be assigned IDs in the range`[len(vocabulary_list), len(vocabulary_list)+num_oov_buckets)` based on a hash of the input value. A positive `num_oov_buckets` can not be specified with `default_value`.
